[Body]
== Description ==
wordcount

== Versions ==
* - base: base version
* - merge: Improve
* - files: files
* - in: in objects
* - wordcount: stable version (LATEST)

== Execution instructions ==

* Main input format:

wordcount.py <DATASET_PATH> <MULTIPLE_FILES> <RESULT_FILE> <BLOCK_SIZE>

where:
    <DATASET_PATH>............ Dataset path/file
                               Available in all versions.
    <MULTIPLE_FILES>.......... Boolean (True if multiple files, False on the contrary)
                               Available in:
                                   - wordcount
    <RESULT_FILE>............. Results file
                               Available in:
                                   - base
                                   - files
                                   - in
                                   - merge
    <BLOCK_SIZE>.............. Block size (only needed if only one file)
                               Available in:
                                   - base
                                   - in
                                   - merge
* Usage in local machine:

    ./run_local.sh

     - Example: ./run_local.sh

* Usage in supercomputer:

    ./launch.sh

    - Example: ./launch.sh

== Build ==
No build is required
